CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 10, 1957, pg. 14 reads: "President OF ABA Victor Daly of Washington, D.C., beams happily with star bridge player Lyda Goggins of Detroit, and Dr. and Mrs. Guy Guinn of Oakland, Calif. Mrs. Guinn is the former Phyllis Clifton of Boston, Mass."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait, from left: Victor Daly, Lyda Goggins, and Phyllis Clifton Guinn, and Dr. Guy Guinn, posed in Fort Pitt Hotel for 24th annual American Bridge Association tournament
